    "title": "Finolex Cables is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "We at Finolex Cables are looking for an experienced Quality Control Engineer based out of Dhanbad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Finolex Cables:\nFinolex Cables is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Finolex Cables!",
